# Sorbet RBIs ARE committed (sorbet/rbi/gems/, sorbet/rbi/annotations/,
# sorbet/rbi/dsl/) so `bundle exec srb tc` is deterministic in CI without
# regenerating from the network. Use `bundle exec tapioca gems` after a
# bundle update to refresh them.

